{"tid":1974381,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"十年，唔會係我地既結局。","createTime":"2020-04-15T20:29:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T21:08:30.000Z","uid":307863,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a5951ce089a3743d8011b300226e90e13568f3af","tid":1974381,"uid":307863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T20:29:42.000Z","msg":"無深入留意過而加既批鬥、花生、人血饅頭、等等，永遠都係集中係行動po上面，其他睇到都唔好擺太多心機係上面，而加我眼中既港人其實最大既主因係被逼到癲，本身抗爭緊突然殺個病毒出黎叫人留係屋企，人既眼睛係雪亮既明顯中共投毒用腦諗下就有答案，但點解無人拎出黎傾下？<br />\n<br />\n因為就算真係傾，都只會停留係(傾下)呢個層面上面，不過到呢度啦，唔會屌都唔想屌手足，只係想你地會多啲分析選擇性吸收，不分化、不割席、不指責，我重講得出口。<br />\n<br />\n最後應承你地應承我自己病毒完，街上見。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命 香港獨立，唯一出路。"},{"pid":"bf1ea72d414ec16219c1f7af1bb15857ee160949","tid":1974381,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T20:38:43.000Z","msg":"大家都等緊23條"},{"pid":"ab9734bbea462a14a0a5040ef7a254528a5a4912","tid":1974381,"uid":355363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T20:40:36.000Z","msg":"想點樣傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e1f0001ed58cfcc18f67dbfdffb6c114f6f5d0","tid":1974381,"uid":307863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf1ea72d414ec16219c1f7af1bb15857ee160949","tid":1974381,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T20:38:43.000Z","msg":"大家都等緊23條"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T20:40:47.000Z","msg":"啲高官一路都想殺曬啲香港人架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76053dae58a26a12300216c9cfa072042efd1584","tid":1974381,"uid":307863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab9734bbea462a14a0a5040ef7a254528a5a4912","tid":1974381,"uid":355363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T20:40:36.000Z","msg":"想點樣傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T20:42:15.000Z","msg":"無架其實講乜都無用，應該要做既都係要做。<br />\n不過上黎r下注意力咁。"},{"pid":"1477feb448712c5a2767b7f020ac45edb29563b8",